dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents parcels for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin on May 14, 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, MilwaukeeCounty_Parcels_20180514.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Milwaukee County Land Information Office in 2018. [polygons representing tax parcels covering Milwaukee County, Wisconsin - one polygon per parcel identifier (TAXKEY) - 'stacked' polygons represent condominium parcels - includes property information attributes]
